            "card_title": "1. Sustainable construction",
            "card_subtitle": "The Grand Soleil BLUE, built with the Composite® technology developed by Italian startup NIcomp, marks a breakthrough in boat construction through the use of thermoplastic resin, a choice that aims to solve one of the most significant problems in the marine industry: end-of-life disposal.",
